is above timetable also support drag n drop

No.

The modules we've created so far are only CRUD modules.

They support:

✅ Create Timetable
✅ Edit Timetable
✅ Delete Timetable
✅ Manage Periods
✅ Manage Bell Schedules
✅ Manage Rooms
✅ Manage Resources
✅ Manage Teachers
✅ Manage Constraints
✅ Manage Workloads
✅ Manage Exam Timetables

But they do NOT yet provide:

❌ Drag & Drop Timetable Grid
❌ Real-time Conflict Detection
❌ Auto Timetable Generation
❌ Teacher Clash Validation
❌ Room Clash Validation
❌ Live Save
❌ Undo / Redo
❌ Timetable Designer UI
❌ Multi-user Editing
❌ Visual Calendar Layout
